  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: `erigon version 2022.07.4-alpha-d88fc824`\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Linux\r\n\r\nCommit hash : \r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nErigon synchronises.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nIt \"does not do anything\". Log shows no activity.\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\nBuild Erigon from source code:\r\n```\r\ngit clone ...\r\ncd erigon\r\nmake erigon\r\n```\r\nStart it on Ropsten:\r\n```\r\n/usr/local/bin/erigon --datadir /data/erigon --chain ropsten --private.api.addr=localhost:9090\r\n```\r\nOr start it on Sepolia:\r\n```\r\n/usr/local/bin/erigon --datadir /data/erigon --chain sepolia --private.api.addr=localhost:9090\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Backtrace\r\n\r\nRopsten:\r\n````\r\n[INFO] [08-03|09:18:15.911] [p2p] GoodPeers                          eth66=33\r\n[INFO] [08-03|09:18:16.581] [txpool] stat                            block=12406745 pending=10000 baseFee=305 queued=29995 alloc=620.2MB sys=1.4GB\r\n[INFO] [08-03|09:19:16.581] [txpool] stat                            block=12406745 pending=10000 baseFee=305 queued=30000 alloc=886.8MB sys=1.4GB\r\n[INFO] [08-03|09:20:15.911] [p2p] GoodPeers                          eth66=33\r\n[INFO] [08-03|09:20:16.580] [txpool] stat                            block=12406745 pending=10000 baseFee=305 queued=30000 alloc=1.0GB sys=1.4GB\r\n[INFO] [08-03|09:21:16.580] [txpool] stat                            block=12406745 pending=10000 baseFee=305 queued=30000 alloc=615.8MB sys=1.4GB\r\n````\r\nSepolia:\r\n```\r\n[INFO] [08-03|09:03:20.763] [p2p] GoodPeers                          eth66=33\r\n[INFO] [08-03|09:03:28.542] [txpool] stat                            block=1453527 pending=2073 baseFee=0 queued=30000 alloc=128.7MB sys=418.7MB\r\n[INFO] [08-03|09:04:28.541] [txpool] stat                            block=1453527 pending=2073 baseFee=0 queued=30000 alloc=138.8MB sys=418.7MB\r\n[INFO] [08-03|09:05:20.763] [p2p] GoodPeers                          eth66=33\r\n[INFO